title: Men's Tennis Falls to Georgia Tech in Opening Round of ITA Kickoff - GoBlueRaiders.com
content: Men's Tennis Falls to Georgia Tech in Opening Round of ITA Kickoff  GoBlueRaiders.com
description: CHARLOTTESVILLE, Va. – After clinching the doubles point to open the dual match against Georgia Tech (3-0), the Yellow Jackets take four singles courts to defeat Middle Tennessee (4-2) 4-2 inside the UVA Tennis Facility at the Boar's Head Resort to begin the ITA Kickoff Weekend.
